defaultThere appear to be two quite different and even contradictory 
defaultnarratives emanating from Government and MPs on this issue at the moment.
default On the one hand the Government has 
defaultlaunched its drive 
defaulttowards pluralised and more localised forms
default of public service provision through the Open Public Services 
defaultagenda
