defaultat it wants charities to participate in this.
defaultYet at the same time statements 
defaultfrom some politicians as part of this debate 
defaultsuggest that large and complex 
defaultcharitable 
defaultorganisations should (and could) be run 
defaultfor free, or that somehow charities should be able 
defaultto attract the skilled leadership they need on a 
defaultpurely 
defaultvoluntary basis.
